    <para id="element-914"><term> Solution </term></para><para id="element-965">Recall that the frequency response of a digital system is periodic with a period of   , with the central period taken as <m:math>
 <m:semantics>
  <m:mrow>
   <m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo> <m:mrow>
    <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>π</m:mi>
   </m:mrow> <m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow>
